    {
      "chinese": "從布農族的傳說故事，也可看出族人如何教育孩童。布農族人非常重視善的德行。例如族人推崇勤勞、謙卑的德性。從很多的故事表達父母親負有傳遞他們的信仰、自然觀、生活禁忌、生活智慧。",
      "ab": "Maca pintaiklac is uvava’az ca bunun, na pakaca’an is paliqabasan a qalinga, mantan ca Bununi’ kasauqbung saduus hinuzangan. Maca paliqabasan na qalinga mangki’ a maqtu’ ishaiqin is uva’az tu ma’az ca kadadu’un ciin ma’az ca kaisamuan, maszang is tu pinqasmav cina pisidungdung is is’ang, misnaca’an paliqabasani’ ca madadaingaz iskungunu nais laituza’an, talmaupa’an, kisamuan ciin taiklac is iniqumican.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2022/02/19/cf1a716622db5c2e3b6b94da2fe2b0e8.wav",
