    {
      "chinese": "布農族的歌謠也反應了我們的生活寫照，有些是描述小孩在大自然中自由自在的玩耍，有些則是反映兒童負擔家務的辛苦。所以無論從故事或是歌謠來看，布農族是重視孩子的。",
      "ab": "Mu’amin ca sintusauc is bununi’ tu maupin amin is tutuza’ a iniqumican, maiza ca palacias sintaldaingan is uvava’az, maiza amin ca kinangu’an maqaipus uvava’az. Daqat maca minaha’an ta paliqabasan ciin sintusauc tan’a saduu, mantan ca bununi’ kasauqbung saduus sintaldaingas uvava’az.",
      "order": "3",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2022/02/19/488b61cdb2ed8e51ee8c634c3215e176.wav",
      "word": [
        {
